Union Armies on the Move!
\tThe citizens of the United States have been calling for action against the rebellion and the President has finally answered this call. Today Lincoln has announced that Union armies are moving into Confederate territory, to engage Confederate armies and to quell the rebellion.\n\tBefore this action was taken, support for the southern cause was steadily increasing in slave states, as Lincoln was seen to be unable to solve the crisis at hand, much like his predecessor Buchanan. However, with Lincoln showing a stronger resolve, many advocates of rebellion have grown concerned.\n\tNow that the people in the United States know that their leadership is acting, the anticipation for action has turned into hope for a quick victory.
